text: Zoe Creed (born 29 March 2001) is an Australian model and beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned Miss Universe Australia 2024. She represented Australia at the Miss Universe 2024 pageant in Mexico. == Pageantry == === Miss Universe Australia 2024 === On September 5, 2024, Creed represented Queensland Miss Universe Australia 2024 pageant and competed against 28 other candidates at Crown Perth in Perth, where she won the title and was succeeded by Miss Universe 2023 second runner-up Moraya Wilson. === Miss Universe 2024 === Creed represented Australia at Miss Universe 2024 pageant to be held in the Arena CDMX, Mexico City, Mexico, on 16 November 2024, but was unplaced. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Beauty pageant winners Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Australian people Category:Australian models
